a.title: File:Flag of Newfoundland and Labrador (construction sheet).svg

p.a: File:Flag of Newfoundland and Labrador (construction sheet).svg

tr.td: Original 2005 upload was created by Robert Crosbie and uploaded by Kooma. Entire flag redrawn/recoded from scratch by MapGrid in 2019. Colors changed by Great Brightstar in 2019.
